headline: TXN- A Resilient Semiconductor Name That's on the March
summary: Resilience. It’s a characteristic that we all aspire to, although some of us are better at being resilient than others. The stock market certainly was in the first half of 2025 – and one of my biggest winners most recently is semiconductor maker Texas Instruments Inc. (TXN), explains Jim Woods, editor of Investing Edge.
